- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses adding an implementation of a communication protocol to existing program analyses, which involves programming language concepts. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possibility as the paper mentions anonymity in the communication model, which could involve security and cryptography considerations. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possibility as the paper discusses abstract interpretation and symbolic execution, which are related to logic in computer science. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possibility as the paper discusses program analyses, which can be viewed as automata that operate on formal languages.
